         Karana is a particular server because all big guilds (something like 30 or so) have subscribe to the KGC (Karana Guild Central) which set up rotations between guilds to allow EVERYBODY to have their shot at all these mobs.</P><P>This have 2 main consequences : we are the last server to kill many mobs, Sleeper not even woke up...but we don't care about patches (of course, as an European, I would prefer patches while sleeping).</P><P>As soon as a mob is too wanted, we set up a rotation on it. Even NToV is on a rotation, 12 guilds able to clear it (rotation starts and ends whith Aary pops).</P><P>Emperor will be on a rotation soon too...</P><P>On other servers, there are less guild able to clear NToV but these guilds are really powerfull...most powerfull guilds on Karana are equal in numbers with an adverage guild on other servers.</P><P>This is more friendly, even with neverending discussions about some FFA rules.</P><P>You can see our rules here (if some of you see in our way to do a good one) : <a href="http://kgc.igz.net" target="_blank">http://kgc.igz.net</a></P><P>KGC exists for more than 2.5 years now and works quite fine...sure we wait too much time between 2 attempts but at least, we are SURE to try it.</P><P></P><P>Edited by - Coercitas on 09/09/2002  06:26:11</P><P>Edited by - Coercitas on 09/09/2002  06:27:05<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
